  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">With the grant funds, The Other Media will establish a Campaign and Resource Centre for Community Environmental Monitoring to support coastal communities in the state of Tamil Nadu by training youth in skills to campaign for environmental health and justice, marine conservation, and customary rights. TOM will enhance the capacity of coastal communities to combat unsustainable development by using and expanding democratic spaces for dissent and proactive engagement by supporting coastal communities to assert their traditional customary rights over coastal and ocean commons. TOM will increase resilience among such communities to the vagaries of uncertain climate future through measures aiming to protect natural coastal formations while increasing awareness among fisher people about sustainable fishing methods and climate change.</narrative>
  </description>
